3
00:00:20.070 --> 00:00:23.196
The four phenomenal warriors.
representing the four galaxies.

4
00:00:23.206 --> 00:00:24.731
who will be special
participants in this.

5
00:00:24.741 --> 00:00:27.267
the Tenkaichi Grand Tournament.

6
00:00:27.277 --> 00:00:29.036
being hosted by world-class
multimillionaire Gyosan Money.

7
00:00:29.046 --> 00:00:31.405
have just arrived on Earth!

8
00:00:31.415 --> 00:00:34.741
Oh. my! Things have already
become more exciting!

9
00:00:34.751 --> 00:00:39.751
This is the first time I've ever seen
an alien. and I am quite impressed!

10
00:00:40.757 --> 00:00:44.217
And so. let us ask some
questions of Mr. Gyosan Money.

11
00:00:44.227 --> 00:00:47.754
What is the Tenkaichi
Grand Tournament. exactly?

12
00:00:47.764 --> 00:00:52.092
My adorable. only son. Doll.
badgered me for this. you see...

13
00:00:52.102 --> 00:00:55.762
It is our present to him
on his tenth birthday.

14
00:00:55.772 --> 00:00:58.765
Papa. are there really going
to be aliens?

15
00:00:58.775 --> 00:01:00.601
Oh. of course.

16
00:01:00.611 --> 00:01:03.370
This will be a raw battle between
the most powerful Earthlings and aliens.

17
00:01:03.380 --> 00:01:06.707
Papa is going to let you watch
it from these special seats.

18
00:01:06.717 --> 00:01:11.378
Doll. as long as you have money
in this world. you can do anything!

19
00:01:11.388 --> 00:01:15.048
P-Producer.
could we ask you to elaborate?

20
00:01:15.058 --> 00:01:18.685
The richest man in the world here.
Mr. Gyosan Money.

21
00:01:18.695 --> 00:01:23.695
is sponsoring the biggest
martial arts tournament ever!

22
00:01:24.735 --> 00:01:26.293
It's a tournament where.

23
00:01:26.303 --> 00:01:27.594
regardless of age. gender.
nationality. pro or amateur status.

24
00:01:27.604 --> 00:01:29.396
the most powerful combat sportsmen...

25
00:01:29.406 --> 00:01:31.498
...in the whole wide
world have been invited.

26
00:01:31.508 --> 00:01:34.401
and they can battle with
each other as hard as they want!

27
00:01:34.411 --> 00:01:37.404
The winner will receive
one hundred million zeni!

28
00:01:37.414 --> 00:01:39.339
Runner-up prizes of tour packages...

29
00:01:39.349 --> 00:01:41.541
for the entire family to the
hot springs resorts of the world...

30
00:01:41.551 --> 00:01:43.410
will also be presented!

31
00:01:43.420 --> 00:01:47.347
What's more. the winner
will meet that hero

32
00:01:47.357 --> 00:01:49.750
that saved humanity from
the terror of the Cell Games.

33
00:01:49.760 --> 00:01:54.760
something that my enormous wealth has
made possible for the first time...

34
00:01:57.768 --> 00:02:01.363
the right to challenge
Mister Satan in the ring!

35
00:02:17.721 --> 00:02:22.920
It's the ultra-gifted. most powerful
combat sportsman on earth. Mister Satan!

36
00:02:40.744 --> 00:02:44.942
So Cell has become the
one who defeated Cell. huh?

37
00:02:46.083 --> 00:02:48.210
That's okay. I guess.

38
00:03:01.431 --> 00:03:06.693
<i>Break through the shining clouds.</i>
<i>and fly away (fly away)</i>

39
00:03:06.703 --> 00:03:14.034
<i>As a panorama spreads</i>
<i>itself throughout my being!</i>

40
00:03:14.044 --> 00:03:19.372
<i>The earth. having been kicked</i>
<i>in the face. gets angry (angry)!</i>

41
00:03:19.382 --> 00:03:26.046
<i>And makes one of its
volcanoes explode!</i>

42
00:03:26.056 --> 00:03:32.719
<i>If. within the thawed polar ice.</i>

43
00:03:32.729 --> 00:03:41.728
<i>There is a dinosaur. then I want</i>
<i>to train him to balance atop a ball.</i>

44
00:03:41.738 --> 00:03:45.065
<i>CHA-LA-HEAD-CHA-LA</i>

45
00:03:45.075 --> 00:03:54.074
<i>No matter what may happen.</i>
<i>I feel as though nothing can bother me.</i>

46
00:03:54.084 --> 00:03:57.744
<i>CHA-LA-HEAD-CHA-LA</i>

47
00:03:57.754 --> 00:04:03.750
<i>However hard your chest pounds.</i>
<i>the Genki Dama will roar!</i>

48
00:04:03.760 --> 00:04:07.087
<i>CHA-LA-HEAD-CHA-LA</i>

49
00:04:07.097 --> 00:04:16.096
<i>The emptier your head is. the more</i>
<i>room there is to pack with dreams.</i>

50
00:04:16.106 --> 00:04:19.432
<i>CHA-LA-HEAD-CHA-LA</i>

51
00:04:19.442 --> 00:04:26.439
<i>With a cheerful face and an Ultra-Z.</i>
<i>today is ai-yai-yai-yai-yai...</i>

52
00:04:26.449 --> 00:04:28.440
<i>Sparking!</i>

53
00:05:05.755 --> 00:05:11.022
"The Galaxy at its Threshold!
A Phenomenally Awesome Guy"

54
00:05:17.456 --> 00:05:19.782
There are exactly 200 contestants
here from all over the world.

55
00:05:19.792 --> 00:05:23.119
confident enough in their abilities to
gather at the Tenkaichi Grand Tournament.

56
00:05:23.129 --> 00:05:26.122
With the chance to challenge the
hero Mister Satan on the line.

57
00:05:26.132 --> 00:05:28.291
the preliminaries are already
being held...

58
00:05:28.301 --> 00:05:30.459
across eight different
battle stages at once!

59
00:05:30.469 --> 00:05:35.464
Each stage has 25 contestants fighting
it out in a Battle Royale format.

60
00:05:35.474 --> 00:05:40.469
and only the last remaining fighter
from each will advance to the semifinals!

61
00:05:40.479 --> 00:05:42.138
As for an explanation to the rules.

62
00:05:42.148 --> 00:05:44.941
contestants who fall from the
battle stage into the sea below.

63
00:05:44.951 --> 00:05:47.810
get knocked out. or give up.
are eliminated.

64
00:05:47.820 --> 00:05:52.548
However. one cannot.
of course. kill another opponent.

65
00:05:52.558 --> 00:05:55.584
Also. the use of weapons is
grounds for disqualification.

66
00:06:13.779 --> 00:06:17.010
I wonder who I should take with me on
my tour of the hot springs of the world.

67
00:06:17.783 --> 00:06:19.775
<i>Gohan-chan!</i>

68
00:06:19.785 --> 00:06:23.112
<i>Gohan-chan.</i> stick it to them!

69
00:06:23.122 --> 00:06:29.186
Huh? Gohan has entered?
But he's a Super Saiyan!

70
00:06:33.799 --> 00:06:40.034
N-not Piccolo. too! I don't suppose
Trunks is here as well. is he?

71
00:06:47.813 --> 00:06:52.113
If it was just Yamucha and Tenshinhan.
I figured this could have turned out.

72
00:06:57.823 --> 00:07:01.150
<i>Chichi-san.</i> I'm surprised
you let <i>Gohan-kun</i> enter.

73
00:07:01.160 --> 00:07:04.720
<i>Gohan-chan</i> does nothin'
but study day in and day out.

74
00:07:04.730 --> 00:07:08.090
If he doesn't keep his strength up.
it'll be all for nothin'.

75
00:07:08.100 --> 00:07:11.093
I was thinkin' it wouldn't be so bad
to let him relax once in a while.

76
00:07:11.103 --> 00:07:14.096
Is that right?
That's parental love for you.

77
00:07:14.106 --> 00:07:16.399
I wanted to take a tour
of the world's hot springs

78
00:07:16.409 --> 00:07:18.100
together with the rest of the family.

79
00:07:18.110 --> 00:07:22.505
and here Trunks had just
come back from the future

80
00:07:22.515 --> 00:07:25.107
to report that he had defeated
No. 17 and No. 18.

81
00:07:25.117 --> 00:07:27.443
so this is a golden opportunity for us!

82
00:07:27.453 --> 00:07:29.445
What's Vegeta doin'?

83
00:07:29.455 --> 00:07:33.849
That man is useless! It's almost
as if he's lost the desire to fight.

84
00:07:33.859 --> 00:07:37.787
and he spends his days
just thinking about stuff.

85
00:07:37.797 --> 00:07:40.493
That's because of <i>Goku-sa</i> dyin'.

86
00:07:43.469 --> 00:07:45.801
<i>Ten-san.</i> go get them!

87
00:07:46.472 --> 00:07:49.131
You too. Kuririn. as long as we're at it.

88
00:07:49.141 --> 00:07:52.907
Oolong. there aren't any
<i>pichi-pichi</i> gals around!

89
00:07:54.814 --> 00:07:56.906
Gramps. what are you looking at?

90
00:07:56.916 --> 00:07:58.808
We came to watch a martial
arts tournament. right?

91
00:07:58.818 --> 00:08:00.776
We don't need to watch

92
00:08:00.786 --> 00:08:03.412
to know that Gohan or Trunks is
obviously going to win. don't we?

93
00:08:03.422 --> 00:08:07.552
That's why I'm on the lookout for
gals with D-cups and T-back thongs!

94
00:08:10.763 --> 00:08:12.594
There they are!

95
00:08:13.766 --> 00:08:14.757
"Bounce"

96
00:08:14.767 --> 00:08:15.756
"Jiggle"

97
00:08:23.776 --> 00:08:27.436
This is even more incredible
than the Tenkaichi Tournament!

98
00:08:27.446 --> 00:08:30.106
You wish you could enter. huh?

99
00:08:30.116 --> 00:08:33.574
But you're a dead man now.

100
00:08:34.120 --> 00:08:37.954
A fight between Gohan and
Trunks is sure to be awesome!

101
00:08:47.466 --> 00:08:51.927
I never would have thought that
Gohan and those guys would enter.

102
00:08:51.937 --> 00:08:55.131
And here I borrowed money
to take a plane here.

103
00:08:55.141 --> 00:08:57.800
I was going to earn a
hundred million zeni. too.

104
00:08:57.810 --> 00:09:01.003
It looks like <i>Yamucha-san</i>
doesn't feel like fighting at all.

105
00:09:01.013 --> 00:09:02.405
There's no helping him. huh?

106
00:09:02.415 --> 00:09:05.408
He's given up on winnin'. after all.

107
00:09:05.418 --> 00:09:08.411
That's right. He can't beat Trunks.

108
00:09:08.421 --> 00:09:10.184
Or <i>Gohan-chan.</i> either!

109
00:09:25.438 --> 00:09:27.065
Disqualified!

110
00:09:28.441 --> 00:09:30.432
Over already?

111
00:09:38.117 --> 00:09:40.009
A long time ago.

112
00:09:40.019 --> 00:09:44.547
Father also entered the Tenkaichi
Tournament and worked on his skills.

113
00:09:44.557 --> 00:09:45.922
so that goes for me. too!

114
00:09:46.792 --> 00:09:49.659
Contestant Son Gohan has
passed the preliminaries!

115
00:09:56.135 --> 00:09:59.036
Contestant Trunks has
passed the preliminaries!

116
00:10:18.157 --> 00:10:19.148
How come?

117
00:10:19.158 --> 00:10:21.456
Contestant Kuririn has
passed the preliminaries!

118
00:10:25.164 --> 00:10:27.598
Contestant Piccolo has
passed the preliminaries!

119
00:10:32.171 --> 00:10:34.401
Contestant Tenshinhan has
passed the preliminaries!

120
00:10:34.840 --> 00:10:36.000
What!?

121
00:10:40.179 --> 00:10:44.673
Contestant Dosukoi. Contestant Udo.
and Contestant Kung Foon have passed!

122
00:10:50.189 --> 00:10:51.780
Mister Satan.

123
00:10:51.790 --> 00:10:54.020
having seen the preliminaries.
what are your impressions?

124
00:10:55.861 --> 00:10:59.855
N-none of them have
had enough training...

125
00:10:59.865 --> 00:11:02.358
The semifinals will consist
of the eight contestants

126
00:11:02.368 --> 00:11:05.201
who passed through the preliminaries
fighting one-on-one against each other.

127
00:11:06.138 --> 00:11:09.098
With Piccolo as my opponent.
luck is not on my side.

128
00:11:09.108 --> 00:11:11.474
Geez. this is the worst!

129
00:11:12.811 --> 00:11:15.971
The first match of the
semifinals will be a fight

130
00:11:15.981 --> 00:11:18.176
between Contestant Son Gohan
and Contestant Udo.

131
00:11:21.153 --> 00:11:25.481
What is this. a kid as my opponent?
This isn't my day.

132
00:11:25.491 --> 00:11:29.587
Hey. kid! I'm not holding back on you.
just because you're little. got it?

133
00:11:30.829 --> 00:11:33.155
Right. understood!

134
00:11:33.165 --> 00:11:36.158
What? Jerk me around. will you?

135
00:11:36.168 --> 00:11:37.829
Why. you!

136
00:11:42.508 --> 00:11:44.601
Attaboy. <i>Gohan-chan!</i>

137
00:11:48.180 --> 00:11:50.039
The second match of the
semifinals will be a fight

138
00:11:50.049 --> 00:11:53.644
between Contestant Trunks
and Contestant Tenshinhan.

139
00:11:55.521 --> 00:12:00.083
Trunks! I'm not letting
you go easy on me!

140
00:12:00.859 --> 00:12:01.859
Right!

141
00:12:14.139 --> 00:12:16.131
T-they're floating in mid-air!

142
00:12:16.141 --> 00:12:18.905
It looks that way to me. too!

143
00:12:24.149 --> 00:12:25.707
<i>Kiko-ho!</i>

144
00:12:57.182 --> 00:13:00.509
M-Mister Satan. how can this be?

145
00:13:00.519 --> 00:13:04.079
Hmph! I-it's all tricks! Like the
quick costume changes in a Kabuki play!

146
00:13:04.089 --> 00:13:06.782
Something like that!

147
00:13:06.792 --> 00:13:11.627
W-what are those guys doing at
a dinky tournament like this?

148
00:13:14.800 --> 00:13:16.961
Sheesh. how worthless!

149
00:13:31.817 --> 00:13:34.285
Contestant Trunks wins!

150
00:13:49.835 --> 00:13:51.827
<i>I-I have to do something!</i>

151
00:13:51.837 --> 00:13:55.329
My. Mister Satan.
you're looking pale.

152
00:13:56.175 --> 00:13:59.168
M-my stomach hurts! Yow-ow-ow-ow!

153
00:13:59.178 --> 00:14:04.106
This won't do! Producer.
take Mister Satan to the dispensary.

154
00:14:04.116 --> 00:14:11.784
I-I'll go by myself. I-I'll be
right back... Yow-ow-ow-ow!

155
00:14:12.458 --> 00:14:15.655
I'd better just go on and scram.

156
00:14:16.795 --> 00:14:20.456
They say that only fools rush in where
angels fear to tread. after all...

157
00:14:20.466 --> 00:14:23.459
Oh. it's Mister Satan!

158
00:14:23.500 --> 00:14:28.500
Satan...! Satan...!

159
00:14:34.146 --> 00:14:39.584
<i>T-this is no time for me</i>
<i>to be doing this!</i>

160
00:14:50.829 --> 00:14:52.988
The third match of the semifinals

161
00:14:52.998 --> 00:14:55.466
will be between Contestant Kuririn
and Contestant Piccolo.

162
00:14:57.836 --> 00:15:02.765
<i>Piccolo wouldn't use his</i>
<i>Makankosappo blast on me. would he?</i>

163
00:15:02.775 --> 00:15:08.680
<i>Piccolo-san!</i> Good luck!
<i>Piccolo-san!</i>

164
00:15:09.448 --> 00:15:13.776
Gohan doesn't need to be
cheering Piccolo on.

165
00:15:13.786 --> 00:15:16.779
After all. there's
no way Kuririn can win.

166
00:15:16.789 --> 00:15:18.347
Dammit!

167
00:15:19.124 --> 00:15:22.582
<i>If this is how it's going to be.</i>
<i>then I'm going to go out big!</i>

168
00:15:30.135 --> 00:15:32.828
What's with that indifferent stance!?

169
00:15:32.838 --> 00:15:37.673
He's doing that to make a fool of me!
He's definitely making a fool of me!

170
00:15:39.144 --> 00:15:41.704
Piccolo!

171
00:15:54.159 --> 00:15:57.820
I thought there were going to be some
guys here with a little fortitude.

172
00:15:57.830 --> 00:16:01.027
I'm not about to stay here and
hang around with you any longer.

173
00:16:14.112 --> 00:16:16.672
As a result of Contestant Piccolo
forfeiting the match.

174
00:16:16.682 --> 00:16:19.082
Contestant Kuririn wins!

175
00:16:19.785 --> 00:16:22.720
Lucky! Bonus. bonus!

176
00:16:23.455 --> 00:16:26.415
Contestant Dosukoi narrowly
turns the tables and wins!

177
00:16:26.425 --> 00:16:30.452
The four contestants who will proceed
to the finals have been decided!

178
00:16:30.462 --> 00:16:33.789
<i>Kaio-sama.</i> what's the situation?

179
00:16:33.799 --> 00:16:38.460
Oh. Gohan and the others are
winning their way through smoothly.

180
00:16:38.470 --> 00:16:40.665
I suppose they would be. huh?

181
00:16:51.483 --> 00:16:57.979
Good grief. there's no way my pupils
could beat those outrageous guys...

182
00:17:01.159 --> 00:17:03.855
I made it! There's the exit!

183
00:17:11.103 --> 00:17:12.502
Mister Satan!

184
00:17:15.107 --> 00:17:19.768
The dispensary is that way.
This way is the exit to Battle Island.

185
00:17:19.778 --> 00:17:24.106
That's fine!
My stomachache is chronic...

186
00:17:24.116 --> 00:17:28.443
It would be best if I had my
personal physician look at me.

187
00:17:28.453 --> 00:17:30.445
B-but what about Mr. Money?

188
00:17:30.455 --> 00:17:33.715
It's all right. it's all right.
I'll be right back.

189
00:17:33.725 --> 00:17:38.162
I'll just dash on over the bridge.
here. and then dash on... dash on...

190
00:17:38.797 --> 00:17:40.697
Huh?

191
00:17:42.467 --> 00:17:45.368
Am I starting to get dizzy. too?

192
00:17:48.473 --> 00:17:52.134
It's gone! It's gone! It's gone!
The bridge is gone!

193
00:17:52.184 --> 00:17:57.184
Satan...! Satan...!

194
00:18:01.486 --> 00:18:06.486
For the finals. we're relocating
the arena to Battle Island II.

195
00:18:06.592 --> 00:18:08.287
We're currently underway.

196
00:18:11.430 --> 00:18:14.423
With the battle stage now
on Battle Island II.

197
00:18:14.433 --> 00:18:16.391
we are just about ready

198
00:18:16.401 --> 00:18:18.760
to hold the finals with these
four powerful competitors.

199
00:18:18.770 --> 00:18:20.635
with a challenge to Mister
Satan at stake!

200
00:18:31.450 --> 00:18:34.681
<i>Gohan-chan!</i>
Stick it to them!

201
00:18:35.120 --> 00:18:36.778
This is embarrassing.

202
00:18:36.788 --> 00:18:41.191
Trunks! Take me along on
that world hot springs tour!

203
00:18:43.795 --> 00:18:47.094
Kuririn! Hang in there
as reasonably as you can!

204
00:18:52.137 --> 00:18:54.463
And now. I shall explain the rules.

205
00:18:54.473 --> 00:18:57.566
There are four specially-built
underground tunnels here.

206
00:18:57.576 --> 00:18:59.801
each one leading to one of the north.
south. east. or west Battle Zones.

207
00:18:59.811 --> 00:19:01.436
The contestants have drawn lots

208
00:19:01.446 --> 00:19:03.739
to determine who will go ride in the
machines for each tunnel and continue on.

209
00:19:03.749 --> 00:19:06.742
until they arrive in their
respective Battle Zone.

210
00:19:06.752 --> 00:19:10.145
Once they do. there will
be a phenomenal warrior.

211
00:19:10.155 --> 00:19:12.748
here all the way from the North.
South. East. and West Galaxies.

212
00:19:12.758 --> 00:19:14.182
who has come here
especially to participate

213
00:19:14.192 --> 00:19:16.592
in the Tenkaichi Grand Tournament.
waiting there for them!

214
00:19:18.764 --> 00:19:20.622
The system continues so that
after defeating that warrior.

215
00:19:20.632 --> 00:19:22.424
whoever gets on the elevator
above them.

216
00:19:22.434 --> 00:19:26.928
and is the first one back here.
at the ground-level center stage.

217
00:19:26.938 --> 00:19:31.500
will be the glorious winner.
and will challenge Mister Satan!

218
00:19:34.112 --> 00:19:36.705
If I can get by without
having to fight Gohan directly.

219
00:19:36.715 --> 00:19:39.843
there's still a good enough
chance left that I could win!

220
00:19:41.787 --> 00:19:44.780
All right. all I have to do is
be the first one back. right?

221
00:19:44.790 --> 00:19:49.451
The final round now starts!
10... 9...

222
00:19:49.461 --> 00:19:51.119
8...

223
00:19:51.129 --> 00:19:52.454
7...

224
00:19:52.464 --> 00:19:54.122
6...

225
00:19:54.132 --> 00:19:55.457
5...

226
00:19:55.467 --> 00:19:56.792
4...

227
00:19:56.802 --> 00:19:58.460
3...

228
00:19:58.470 --> 00:19:59.795
2...

229
00:19:59.805 --> 00:20:01.463
1...

230
00:20:01.473 --> 00:20:02.770
0!

231
00:20:13.819 --> 00:20:18.620
Please enjoy the fight in the
Battle Zone on the monitor screens.

232
00:20:30.836 --> 00:20:33.464
I-I'm going to wet myself!

233
00:21:20.152 --> 00:21:23.553
So this is the Battle Zone. huh?

234
00:21:33.498 --> 00:21:35.966
Are you my opponent!?

235
00:21:39.504 --> 00:21:43.832
I've already faced Piccolo today.
and my luck is running strong.

236
00:21:43.842 --> 00:21:48.870
It sure is unlucky for you to
have to fight me like this.

237
00:21:51.850 --> 00:21:55.684
S-she's so cu~ute!

238
00:21:57.189 --> 00:21:58.613
B-but still.

239
00:21:58.623 --> 00:22:01.183
just because you're a woman.
you won't get any mercy from me!

240
00:22:01.193 --> 00:22:03.627
I'm going to be the first one back!

241
00:22:26.484 --> 00:22:29.248
W-who are you!?

242
00:22:34.492 --> 00:22:36.551
K-Kuririn!

243
00:22:44.836 --> 00:22:47.495
<i>Dosukoi! Dosukoi!</i>

244
00:22:47.505 --> 00:22:50.165
<i>Dosukoi! Dosukoi!</i>

245
00:22:50.175 --> 00:22:54.976
<i>Dosukoi... Dosu... koi...</i>

246
00:23:08.793 --> 00:23:10.658
He killed him!

247
00:23:26.144 --> 00:23:28.470
What's going on here!?

248
00:23:28.480 --> 00:23:30.472
Dear. this is going too far!

249
00:23:30.482 --> 00:23:34.142
P-Producer.
what is the meaning of this!?

250
00:23:34.152 --> 00:23:37.245
I-I didn't invite those guys!

251
00:23:37.255 --> 00:23:41.483
The Galactic Warriors I arranged
for were Mister Satan's pupils!

252
00:23:41.493 --> 00:23:43.290
How could they have
switched places so quickly?

253
00:23:44.162 --> 00:23:45.459
Mama!

254
00:23:47.165 --> 00:23:48.132
What!?

255
00:24:13.124 --> 00:24:18.053
Haven't you got things backward here!?
This is just a game!

256
00:24:18.063 --> 00:24:19.690
We're not out to kill each other!

257
00:24:29.808 --> 00:24:31.605
Who are you!?

258
00:24:36.147 --> 00:24:39.412
Would it be enough if I said
I was just a Galactic Warrior?

259
00:25:54.159 --> 00:25:57.152
Stop that! This is a
martial arts tournament!

260
00:25:57.162 --> 00:25:59.858
You're saying this is a game?

261
00:26:06.438 --> 00:26:08.201
What's going on?

262
00:26:13.778 --> 00:26:18.073
Mister Satan!
Everything depends on your power now!

263
00:26:18.083 --> 00:26:20.442
Please help us somehow! We beg you!

264
00:26:20.452 --> 00:26:24.112
J-just hang on a second!
My stomach still hurts!

265
00:26:24.122 --> 00:26:28.249
<i>If I can buy some time here. then those</i>
<i>other guys should defeat them for me.</i>

266
00:26:28.259 --> 00:26:30.489
<i>They defeated Cell. after all.</i>

267
00:26:56.488 --> 00:26:58.581
Are you finished already?

268
00:27:04.429 --> 00:27:06.158
Die!

269
00:27:38.796 --> 00:27:40.855
W- what is this?

270
00:27:43.801 --> 00:27:45.530
That's an incredible <i>Ki!</i>

271
00:27:49.807 --> 00:27:53.134
Mister Satan! Hurry! Hurry!

272
00:27:53.144 --> 00:27:57.472
Don't be so impatient!
I'm just wiping now!

273
00:27:57.500 --> 00:28:02.500
Satan...! Satan...!
Satan...! Satan...!

274
00:28:18.102 --> 00:28:20.263
Thank goodness!

275
00:28:24.108 --> 00:28:26.167
Ladies and gentlemen.
please be at ease!

276
00:28:26.177 --> 00:28:30.438
Our hero. Mister Satan. is setting
forth to put down these bad guys!

277
00:28:30.448 --> 00:28:32.340
Everything is all right now!

278
00:28:32.350 --> 00:28:36.684
Please observe the monitor screens
to see Mister Satan in action!

279
00:28:41.793 --> 00:28:43.785
H- hurry up and start this thing!

280
00:28:43.795 --> 00:28:44.452
Right!

281
00:28:44.462 --> 00:28:46.794
Wait! I haven't fastened the seatbelt!

282
00:28:47.465 --> 00:28:50.059
Earth is in a great pinch.

283
00:28:51.135 --> 00:28:54.462
Who would have figured on Bojack?

284
00:28:54.472 --> 00:28:56.464
Bojack?

285
00:28:56.474 --> 00:29:00.668
Long ago. he was a thug.
brimming with an evil <i>Ki.</i>

286
00:29:00.678 --> 00:29:02.737
who wandered the North.
South. East. and West Galaxies.

287
00:29:02.747 --> 00:29:06.407
attempting to destroy each
one of them.

288
00:29:06.417 --> 00:29:08.409
You mean someone like
Piccolo Daimao?

289
00:29:08.419 --> 00:29:13.748
He was a bloodthirsty devil. with an
evil <i>Ki</i> far greater than Piccolo Daimao.

290
00:29:13.758 --> 00:29:17.352
As such. the four of us Kaio.
from the north. south. east. and west.

291
00:29:17.362 --> 00:29:18.753
put our powers together.

292
00:29:18.763 --> 00:29:22.423
and sealed him up on a planet
at the far end of the galaxy.

293
00:29:22.433 --> 00:29:24.759
Sealed him up on a planet at
the far end of the galaxy?

294
00:29:24.769 --> 00:29:27.295
Goku. this is your fault.

295
00:29:27.305 --> 00:29:31.733
By wrecking my Kaio World
during the fight with Cell.

296
00:29:31.743 --> 00:29:35.770
and causing me to die.
the seal has been broken.

297
00:29:35.780 --> 00:29:39.440
But to think that Bojack would
set his sights on Earth!

298
00:29:39.450 --> 00:29:43.045
But then. <i>Kaio-sama.</i>
Earth still has Gohan!

299
00:29:51.129 --> 00:29:53.188
<i>K- Kuririn-san!</i>

300
00:30:01.806 --> 00:30:04.799
<i>Trunks-san! Kuririn-san!</i>

301
00:30:04.809 --> 00:30:08.643
Hey. kid. Earth is a nice planet. huh?

302
00:30:25.163 --> 00:30:27.597
What an incredible battle power!

303
00:30:30.168 --> 00:30:31.931
Gohan!

304
00:30:33.838 --> 00:30:38.866
A- are these the guys who killed
the four Galactic Warriors?

305
00:30:42.513 --> 00:30:46.745
From now on. this planet
belongs to <i>Bojack-sama.</i>

306
00:30:50.521 --> 00:30:51.846
Ridiculous!

307
00:30:51.856 --> 00:30:54.515
You think we're just going
to let you have it your way?

308
00:30:54.525 --> 00:30:58.186
<i>Bojack-sama</i> is invincible
throughout the galaxy!

309
00:30:58.196 --> 00:31:00.888
For Earth. the greatest planet
in the Northern Galaxy.

310
00:31:00.898 --> 00:31:02.790
most beautiful of all...

311
00:31:02.800 --> 00:31:06.861
...he is the most deserving
being to rule over it.

312
00:31:08.139 --> 00:31:11.466
We will kill anyone who defies him.

313
00:31:11.476 --> 00:31:14.570
Don't go downplaying us!

314
00:31:43.007 --> 00:31:44.474
You'll pay for this!

315
00:32:40.498 --> 00:32:42.156
Not bad. kid.

316
00:32:42.166 --> 00:32:45.026
But with that level of fighting power.
you'll never beat us.

317
00:32:45.036 --> 00:32:47.095
no matter how hard you try!

318
00:33:08.059 --> 00:33:09.116
This is going to be a problem!

319
00:33:09.126 --> 00:33:13.324
Gohan! Get angry!
Show them your true power!

320
00:33:34.151 --> 00:33:36.517
D- damn...

321
00:34:00.177 --> 00:34:01.644
<i>Piccolo-san!</i>

322
00:34:03.447 --> 00:34:07.144
Looks like someone with a
bit of a backbone showed up.

323
00:34:40.818 --> 00:34:42.479
Damn it!

324
00:34:46.157 --> 00:34:47.886
<i>Piccolo-san!</i>

325
00:34:55.166 --> 00:34:58.567
I'm going to get you back
good for what you did earlier!

326
00:35:44.482 --> 00:35:46.140
Dad!

327
00:35:46.150 --> 00:35:48.710
I'll defeat this one!

328
00:36:06.103 --> 00:36:07.866
<i>Vegeta-san...!</i>

329
00:36:31.128 --> 00:36:33.721
Dad had utterly lost the will
to fight after <i>Goku-san</i> died.

330
00:36:33.731 --> 00:36:38.759
and yet here he is. helping me
and <i>Gohan-san</i> during this crisis!

331
00:36:55.820 --> 00:36:58.414
Trunks. you keep out of this!

332
00:37:08.766 --> 00:37:11.759
Dad. you can't do any more
in your condition!

333
00:37:11.769 --> 00:37:15.096
I-I thought I told you
to stay out of this!

334
00:37:15.106 --> 00:37:17.098
<i>Piccolo-san!</i>

335
00:37:17.108 --> 00:37:22.307
D-don't concern yourself with me.
defeat that guy!

336
00:37:22.780 --> 00:37:23.940
Right!

337
00:37:44.135 --> 00:37:46.228
Damn!

338
00:37:47.471 --> 00:37:49.405
<i>Vegeta-san!</i>

339
00:37:50.808 --> 00:37:53.606
You'll have to face me!

340
00:37:59.483 --> 00:38:00.474
<i>Gohan-chan!</i>

341
00:38:00.484 --> 00:38:01.809
Trunks!

342
00:38:01.819 --> 00:38:04.745
W-wait! I still haven't
fastened my seatbelt!

343
00:38:04.755 --> 00:38:06.086
Start!

344
00:38:13.764 --> 00:38:15.254
Take this!

345
00:38:58.809 --> 00:39:04.405
Our telekinesis gives rise to a
containment zone. binding your power!

346
00:39:04.415 --> 00:39:09.182
The more you struggle.
the more your power drops!

347
00:39:17.094 --> 00:39:20.860
Kid. you fought well. I commend you.

348
00:39:56.800 --> 00:39:58.792
<i>Satan-san!</i>

349
00:39:58.802 --> 00:40:01.795
It looks like your life got
extended just a little bit.

350
00:40:01.805 --> 00:40:04.103
Damn you!

351
00:40:11.482 --> 00:40:14.747
<i>Kaio-sama.</i> ain't there
anything we can do!?

352
00:40:37.174 --> 00:40:40.868
Can you see your father
in the Next World yet?

353
00:40:40.878 --> 00:40:44.939
The two of you will enjoy the show
of carnage that is about to begin.

354
00:40:45.516 --> 00:40:47.450
<i>Kaio-sama!</i>

355
00:41:14.478 --> 00:41:17.276
F-Father...

356
00:41:24.488 --> 00:41:27.147
I can't take it any more!

357
00:41:27.157 --> 00:41:30.558
Goku! You're dead!

358
00:41:36.166 --> 00:41:37.963
<i>You ain't going to get
away with this!</i>

359
00:41:38.836 --> 00:41:40.326
What!?

360
00:41:49.513 --> 00:41:54.473
Gohan! Show him your true power!

361
00:41:57.187 --> 00:41:59.513
Father...

362
00:41:59.523 --> 00:42:04.984
Stop acting like such a pampered baby!
You have to protect the earth!

363
00:42:10.467 --> 00:42:12.458
Father!

364
00:42:23.480 --> 00:42:26.176
W-what was that just now!?

365
00:42:49.840 --> 00:42:53.367
Father saved me!

366
00:43:13.797 --> 00:43:18.461
And he said you weren't
going to get away with this!

367
00:43:21.472 --> 00:43:25.602
He told me to protect the earth!

368
00:44:00.177 --> 00:44:03.146
Bujin! Bido!

369
00:45:34.137 --> 00:45:36.799
Dammit!

370
00:45:59.830 --> 00:46:03.090
D-damn!

371
00:46:03.100 --> 00:46:07.093
How could a kid like
you do this to me!?

372
00:46:11.441 --> 00:46:14.434
And then... and then...

373
00:46:14.444 --> 00:46:17.607
...he told me to stop acting
like some pampered baby!

374
00:47:30.787 --> 00:47:33.113
Gohan. you did fine!

375
00:47:33.123 --> 00:47:36.684
Goku. you still acted
recklessly. huh?

376
00:47:37.794 --> 00:47:40.454
<i>Kaio-sama.</i> did I do something?

377
00:47:40.464 --> 00:47:44.491
Oh. I must have blinked.
so I can't be sure.

378
00:47:51.475 --> 00:47:55.138
"Satan saves the earth a
2nd time." huh?

379
00:47:55.812 --> 00:47:59.139
Just once. I'd like to give
him a good talking-to.

380
00:47:59.149 --> 00:48:01.541
It's okay. isn't it?

381
00:48:01.551 --> 00:48:05.078
There's no question that he did
help me out there. after all.

382
00:48:05.088 --> 00:48:09.024
In the end. he defended his
title of "World's Greatest Fool!"

383
00:48:14.097 --> 00:48:16.089
Father?

384
00:48:16.099 --> 00:48:18.759
Gohan. all things considered.
you were something else!

385
00:48:18.769 --> 00:48:20.293
You single-handedly defeated the guy

386
00:48:20.303 --> 00:48:23.096
that neither Piccolo nor Vegeta
could stand up to!

387
00:48:23.106 --> 00:48:25.432
It wasn't single-handed. Father...

388
00:48:25.442 --> 00:48:27.100
Goku came back to life!?

389
00:48:27.110 --> 00:48:29.770
I'm joking! I'm joking!

390
00:48:29.780 --> 00:48:33.440
Why. you scoundrel!
At a time like this!?

391
00:48:33.450 --> 00:48:39.184
"At the second Tenkaichi Grand Tournament.
you too can challenge Satan!"

392
00:48:40.351 --> 00:48:47.015
<i>You're moving on.</i>
<i>beyond the galaxy.</i>

393
00:48:47.025 --> 00:48:51.758
<i>Toward the land of light.</i>
<i>you're rising high!</i>

394
00:48:54.032 --> 00:49:01.029
<i>Summer brings its light
with it for us.</i>

395
00:49:01.039 --> 00:49:06.367
<i>It's new. and yet</i>
<i>for some reason. familiar.</i>

396
00:49:06.377 --> 00:49:15.376
<i>We feel the strong sunlight</i>
<i>hitting our cheeks.</i>

397
00:49:15.386 --> 00:49:24.052
<i>And our courage flows
through us now!</i>

398
00:49:24.062 --> 00:49:26.354
<i>Let's fly!</i>

399
00:49:26.364 --> 00:49:37.732
<i>The blue of the brightly shining sky</i>
<i>and sea swims within our eyes!</i>

400
00:49:37.742 --> 00:49:39.867
<i>Net sky!</i>

401
00:49:39.877 --> 00:49:51.012
<i>Raising our hands high. up to
the light. we connect with it!</i>

402
00:49:51.022 --> 00:49:57.518
<i>Some day. our smiles</i>
<i>will reach there. too.</i>

403
00:49:59.364 --> 00:50:06.027
<i>I'm moving on.</i>
<i>beyond the galaxy.</i>

404
00:50:06.037 --> 00:50:12.533
<i>Toward the land of light.</i>
<i>I'm rising high. rising high!</i>

405
00:50:19.050 --> 00:50:25.114
The End

406
